    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at Gradation 1 per the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements table. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The Claim and Requirement documentation specifies the intended use scope as FDA 510(k) submission support for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump operating in adult CPB at flows of 2–6 L/min and speeds of 2500–3500 RPM.",
